article.description: — Nicolas Timberlake scored 25 points, hitting seven 3-pointers, and Towson defeated James Madison 95-59 on Saturday.
article.headline: Towson rolls past James Madison 95-59
article.story: HARRISONBURG, Va. -- — Nicolas Timberlake scored 25 points, hitting seven 3-pointers, and Towson defeated James Madison 95-59 on Saturday. Antonio Rizzuto added 14 points and Cameron Holden had 12 points with 13 rebounds for the Tigers (23-7, 14-3 Colonial Athletic Association). The Tigers made 14 of 25 3-point attempts. Terrence Edwards scored 29 points for the Dukes (15-14, 6-12). ----
